VegGuide,org,provides,a,user,rated,directory,of,vegan,vegetarian,and,vegan,friendly,restaurants,and,stores,around,the,world,The,site,is,searchable,by,location,and,by,business,The,VegGuide,API,allows,users,to,add,new,restaurant,stores,comments,images,and,all,parts,of,the,core,data,structure,The,API,also,allows,users,to,search,by,region,and,get,reviews,of,entries,The,service,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,JSON